{"tid":27441,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"關於router/網速既疑問","createTime":"2016-12-07T10:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T04:28:20.000Z","uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb37e99f1976338e242a7556d483e12fefc5c90","tid":27441,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"想問下我依家set左兩個wifi<br />\n一個係2.4ghz 一個係5ghz<br />\n<br />\n我部電腦既wifi冇ac得n，咁應該用2.4定5果個會快d？（假設冇好勁既穿透問題，兩者都係收2-3格）<br />\n定係唔關ac/n事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我用iphone 6s做speedtest，用5既速度快過用2.4一半，係唔係5ghz必然快過2.4ghz？<br />\n<br />\n另外我係用緊hkbn bb100，經router後既網速通常係幾多Mbps?<br />\n<br />\n最近先對router有少少認識，想認識多d<br />\n可能問得好白痴，唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7e4dc97828438e4742b6a9a2bdb5f1b03db6a7","tid":27441,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94fc976ca7963738417fd63ea516fa24aff708d","tid":27441,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d22aeede7f1d83d6768d20a123e1f81f930ad5","tid":27441,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"但5hz唔穩定  ping高"},{"pid":"b4dfd86bcfa29637ab14d2bcd5e4db3ed22f1db8","tid":27441,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"行5Ghz , 設備一定要行到AC<br />\n速度正常係行番佢比你嘅8-9成<br />\n你得100M,經番router出黎都唔會差好遠"},{"pid":"d5d14a9f7afe1c0db20315e05f36414ecb7b3084","tid":27441,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"Bb100經wifi你打個八折啦"},{"pid":"71c065edff83d1075cd3a4169bf6d334effa535d","tid":27441,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行5Ghz , 設備一定要行到AC<br />\n速度正常係行番佢比你嘅8-9成<br />\n你得100M,經番router出黎都唔會差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝3位巴打既解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我依家部macbook係冇ac，最高行n既，但佢都收到5ghz果個wifi，而且speedtest都係快2.4一半<br />\n咁我照用5ghz應該都冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一個問題，依家個modem  Ethernet果盞燈+lan線位盞燈長閃，係咪正常？<br />\n因為晏晝佢好似係長著，唔係閃燈<br />\n但依家wifi係冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d419a00e6f4f19706aeb6b5fadb41237bf83c6a2","tid":27441,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>行5Ghz , 設備一定要行到AC<br />\n速度正常係行番佢比你嘅8-9成<br />\n你得100M,經番router出黎都唔會差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝3位巴打既解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我依家部macbook係冇ac，最高行n既，但佢都收到5ghz果個wifi，而且speedtest都係快2.4一半<br />\n咁我照用5ghz應該都冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一個問題，依家個modem  Ethernet果盞燈+lan線位盞燈長閃，係咪正常？<br />\n因為晏晝佢好似係長著，唔係閃燈<br />\n但依家wifi係冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上到網就得啦<br />\n閃緊係傳輸緊數據"},{"pid":"ab347ca8b5483c8910f9fef459e7c854252a5af5","tid":27441,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>行5Ghz , 設備一定要行到AC<br />\n速度正常係行番佢比你嘅8-9成<br />\n你得100M,經番router出黎都唔會差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝3位巴打既解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我依家部macbook係冇ac，最高行n既，但佢都收到5ghz果個wifi，而且speedtest都係快2.4一半<br />\n咁我照用5ghz應該都冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一個問題，依家個modem  Ethernet果盞燈+lan線位盞燈長閃，係咪正常？<br />\n因為晏晝佢好似係長著，唔係閃燈<br />\n但依家wifi係冇問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上到網就得啦<br />\n閃緊係傳輸緊數據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}